      <title>七与我准备将 7-11 便利店与原来的伊藤洋华堂店分开</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/seven-i-climbs-on-reports-it-will-sell-ito-yokado-stores-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七与i Holdings Co. 正在考虑将伊藤洋华堂（该公司历史悠久的超市零售核心）上市，并最终将其从利润更高、增长更快的 7-11 特许经营权中剥离出来，集中精力将便利店打造成全球业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/seven-i-climbs-on-reports-it-will-sell-ito-yokado-stores-unit</guid>
